# Raw pasta

This is a great recipe.

## Sauce

80g Fresh basil
1/3C Olive oil
1C Nuts (half pine nuts, half cashew)
5 Garlic Cloves
1/3C Nutritional yeast
1/2tsp Salt
1/2tsp Black pepper


## Pasta (for 3 people)
3 Medium Zucchini, spiralised
60g Capers
3 Pink radish
3 Big avocadoes
100g Tomatoes OR 30g Sundried tomatoes
30g spinach
30g fresh basil

